Francis Dougherty, et al., Respondents v. Henry J. McGuckin, impleaded, Appellant. Decided March 5, 1890. Appeal from a judgment entered on the report of a referee. Daniel P. Mahony, for appellant. Hector M. Hitchings, for respondents.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J., and Freedman, J.

Per Curiam.

Judgment affirmed with costs.
